net.edzard.kinetic

Class Colour

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.edzard.kinetic.Colour
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, FillStyle

    public class Colour
extends java.lang.Object
implements FillStyle, java.io.Serializable
    A RGBA colour value. Used for defining all sorts of colours using red, green, blue and alpha (opacity) components.
    Author:
    Ed
